{{!< master}}
{{#contentFor "bodyAttr"}}ng-controller="HomeController"{{/contentFor}}

<section class="what-we-are" ng-class="homeBack">
    <div class="wrap">
        <div class="box colour1">
            <h2>We love software</h2>
            <p>We create custom, web software.  We can help you navigate technical complexity to solve your problems and see your ideas evolve into working solutions.  We designing and rolling out custom enterprise and web-based solutions across the world.</p>
            <p>We understand the challenges and opportunities your business faces. And it’s our business to help you succeed, while saving you time and money. We keep technology simple, but offer expert help and resources should you need them.</p>
            <p><a href="about">Learn more about us ›</a></p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
<section class="what-we-work">
        <carousel interval="myInterval">
            <slide ng-repeat="work in works" active="work.active" class="wrap">
                <h2><a href="{{angular 'work.home'}}" ng-bind="work.title" target="_blank"></a></h2>
                <div class="carousel-caption">
                    <p ng-bind="work.description"></p>
                </div>
                <img ng-src="{{angular 'work.image'}}" style="height: 500px">
            </slide>
        </carousel>
</section>
<section class="what-we-love">
    <div class="wrap">
        <h2>What we love</h2>
        <ul>
            <li class="end">
                <div class="illustration fa fa-codepen"></div>
                <p>We love learning, developing and pushing ourselves and we embrace the latest ideas through lots of industry reading and conference-going.</p>
            </li>
            <li>
                <div class="illustration fa fa-code"></div>
                <p>We love Java, C#, Object C, JavaScript, CSS, HTML language. We use Jquery, AngularJs, Node.js, Express, Asp.net, JSP,MSSQL, MySQL, Oracle, MongoDB, Couchbase to create web site</p>
            </li>
            <li>
                <div class="illustration fa fa-apple"></div>
                <p>We love Apple products. We use our Macbooks Pros, iPads and iPhones for work because we love using beautifully designed things.</p>
            </li>
            <li class="last">
                <div class="illustration fa fa-group"></div>
                <p>We love being a professional team and working directly with you on all your projects. We love to talk and discover your ideas.</p>
            </li>
        </ul>
        <a href="project" title="submit your project plan to us" target="_self"><i class="fa fa-hand-o-right"></i> Submit your project plan to us</a>
    </div>
</section>
<section class="cta">
    <div class="wrap">
        <p>Learn how we can help your startup take off. <a href="contact">Get in touch with us ›</a></p>
    </div>
</section>

